---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="Yilong Scrubs | 30+ Year Medical Scrubs Manufacturer & OEM Supplier" 
  description="Premium medical scrubs manufacturer since 1994. ISO 9001/14001/45001 + OEKO-TEX certified. SGS verified factory. Low MOQ from 10 sets. OEM/ODM, private label. Ships worldwide DDP."
  keywords="medical scrubs manufacturer, ISO 9001 hospital uniform factory, nursing scrubs wholesale, OEM/ODM scrub factory, private label medical uniforms"
>

  <!-- ==================== MODULE 1: HERO ==================== -->
  <section class="relative h-[90vh] md:h-[700px] flex items-center bg-primary text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img 
        src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/Aa8c317d768c143bf98a8a63a6a5de8f34.png" 
        alt="Yilong Medical Scrubs Manufacturing" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover" 
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-primary/85 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 z-10 py-16 md:py-0">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-secondary/20 border border-secondary/30 text-secondary text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] rounded-full mb-6">
          Factory Direct · 30+ Years Manufacturing Expertise
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-4 leading-tight">
          Premium Medical Scrubs<br/>
          <span class="text-secondary">Manufacturer · 30+ Years Expertise</span>
        </h1>
        <!-- Certification tagline: P1 priority -->
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-slate-200 mb-2 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          OEKO-TEX® certified · ISO 9001/14001/45001 · SGS verified · 60+ countries
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-300 mb-8">
          Medical scrubs are what we do best. 30 years. Deep focus. Zero distractions.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row flex-wrap gap-3 mt-2">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-secondary px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-base hover:bg-emerald-600 transition shadow-xl text-center">
            Get a Quote →
          </a>
          <a href="/catalog" class="bg-white/10 border border-white/30 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-base hover:bg-white/20 transition text-center flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
            </svg>
            View Product Catalog
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats Bar -->
  <section class="bg-slate-900 text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 divide-x divide-slate-800">
        <div class="py-8 md:py-10 text-center px-4">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">30+</div>
          <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Years Manufacturing</p>
        </div>
        <div class="py-8 md:py-10 text-center px-4">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">60+</div>
          <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Countries Served</p>
        </div>
        <div class="py-8 md:py-10 text-center px-4">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">ISO</div>
          <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">9001/14001/45001</p>
        </div>
        <div class="py-8 md:py-10 text-center px-4">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">10 Sets</div>
          <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Low MOQ · Ships Worldwide</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== MODULE 0.5: TRUST BADGES (P1) ==================== -->
  <section class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200 py-5">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-x-8 gap-y-3 text-center">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-[9px] font-black">✓</div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700">OEKO-TEX® Standard 100</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 bg-blue-600 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white text-[8px] font-black">ISO</div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700">ISO 9001:2015</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 bg-blue-600 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white text-[8px] font-black">ISO</div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700">ISO 14001:2015</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 bg-blue-600 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white text-[8px] font-black">ISO</div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700">ISO 45001:2018</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 bg-red-600 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white text-[9px] font-black">SGS</div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700">SGS Factory Verified</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 bg-secondary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-[9px] font-black">✓</div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700">100% Pre-Shipment QC</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== MODULE 2: FABRIC TIER COMPARISON ==================== -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-4">Fabric Collection</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4">Choose Your Fabric Tier</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-xl mx-auto">Three performance tiers engineered for different global markets. Every fabric is OEKO-TEX® certified.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        
        <!-- Premium -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-secondary shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition relative">
          <div class="bg-secondary text-white text-center py-3 px-4">
            <p class="font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Premium Series</p>
            <p class="text-xs opacity-80">Targeting FIGs Market</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-green-50 text-green-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full mb-3">205 GSM</div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs font-mono leading-relaxed">72% Polyester<br/>21% Rayon<br/>7% Spandex</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 mb-6">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><span class="text-green-500 font-black">✓</span> Ultra-soft, silky drape</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><span class="text-green-500 font-black">✓</span> 4-way stretch & recovery</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><span class="text-green-500 font-black">✓</span> Comfortable & breathable</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><span class="text-green-500 font-black">✓</span> Skin-friendly, OEKO-TEX certified</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4 mb-6">
              <p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700 mb-1">Best For:</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">D2C brands, US/Canada market, ecommerce sellers, private label programs</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="text-secondary font-black text-sm mb-3">→ Recommended for building your own brand</p>
              <a href="/products" class="block bg-secondary text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition text-center">View Premium Collection</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Standard -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="bg-slate-800 text-white text-center py-3 px-4">
            <p class="font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Standard Series</p>
            <p class="text-xs opacity-70">Wholesale Volume Preferred</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full mb-3">180 GSM</div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs font-mono leading-relaxed">Polyester / Spandex<br/>Blend</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 mb-6">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><span class="text-blue-500 font-black">✓</span> Durable and comfortable</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><span class="text-blue-500 font-black">✓</span> High value for money</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><span class="text-blue-500 font-black">✓</span> Easy care, machine washable</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><span class="text-blue-500 font-black">✓</span> OEKO-TEX certified</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4 mb-6">
              <p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700 mb-1">Best For:</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Hospital groups, clinics, distributors, government procurement</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-3">→ Recommended for large-volume stable replenishment</p>
              <a href="/products" class="block bg-slate-800 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-slate-700 transition text-center">View Standard Collection</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Lightweight -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="bg-slate-400 text-white text-center py-3 px-4">
            <p class="font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Lightweight Series</p>
            <p class="text-xs opacity-80">Tropical / Budget Markets</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-orange-50 text-orange-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full mb-3">130 GSM</div>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs font-mono leading-relaxed">Polyester / Spandex<br/>Lightweight Blend</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 mb-6">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><span class="text-orange-500 font-black">✓</span> Lightweight & breathable</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><span class="text-orange-500 font-black">✓</span> Quick-dry fabric</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><span class="text-orange-500 font-black">✓</span> Durable, wash-resistant</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600"><span class="text-orange-500 font-black">✓</span> Budget-friendly</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4 mb-6">
              <p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700 mb-1">Best For:</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Philippines, Middle East, Africa, South America, hot climates</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-3">→ Recommended for hot climate markets</p>
              <a href="/products" class="block bg-slate-600 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-slate-700 transition text-center">View Lightweight Collection</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-xs text-slate-400 mt-6">All three tiers are OEKO-TEX® Standard 100 certified · Each fabric tested for safety before use</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== MODULE 3: CORE VALUE PROPOSITIONS ==================== -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-4">Why Yilong</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4">Why 60+ Countries Choose Us</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-xl mx-auto">Numbers don't lie. SGS tested. Third-party verified.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🏭</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">30+ Years of Focus</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">We have never made anything but medical scrubs. 30 years of formula refinement and production expertise — all in one product category.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-secondary font-bold">Serving 6 continents worldwide</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🧪</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">72/21/7 Premium Fabric</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">205 GSM high-density 4-way stretch fabric. OEKO-TEX® certified. Color fastness Grade 4–5. Shrinkage &lt;0.5%. Lab tested 40+ wash cycles by SGS.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-secondary font-bold">OEKO-TEX® + SGS tested</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🦠</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">Antibacterial &gt;99.9% (SGS)</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">Silver ion antibacterial finishing. Lab verified &gt;99.9% reduction against E. coli and S. aureus per AATCC 100-2019 (SGS tested).</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-secondary font-bold">Available as optional upgrade · Min. 200 sets</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📦</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">Low MOQ — Startup Friendly</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">Color MOQ from 10 sets/color. Sizes freely mixed within each color. Logo customization from 20 sets/style. Industry norm is 50–200 sets/color.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-secondary font-bold">Small order? No problem.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🎨</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">7 Logo Branding Methods</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">Embroidery, screen printing, heat transfer, DTG, foil stamp, pad print, sublimation. One-stop-shop for all your branding needs.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-secondary font-bold">Custom packaging also available</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🌍</div>
          <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">DDP Shipping Worldwide</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">Sea / air / express. DDP (freight + customs + duties included) for USA, Canada, Mexico, LATAM, and the Middle East. No surprise fees at delivery.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-secondary font-bold">Door-to-door service</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== MODULE 4: PRODUCT CATEGORY QUICK LINKS ==================== -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-4">Our Collections</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4">What We Make</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-xl mx-auto">Four product categories. Three fabric tiers. Built for healthcare professionals worldwide.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <a href="/products" class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-[3/4] bg-slate-800 block">
          <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/Aa8c317d768c143bf98a8a63a6a5de8f34.png" alt="Scrub Sets" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500 opacity-60" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-black text-xl mb-1">Scrub Sets</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Top + Pants combos</p>
            <span class="mt-2 text-secondary text-xs font-bold group-hover:underline">Browse →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/products" class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-[3/4] bg-slate-800 block">
          <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/Aa8c317d768c143bf98a8a63a6a5de8f34.png" alt="Jogger Scrubs" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500 opacity-60" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-black text-xl mb-1">Jogger Scrubs</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Modern fit with elastic cuffs</p>
            <span class="mt-2 text-secondary text-xs font-bold group-hover:underline">Browse →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/products" class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-[3/4] bg-slate-800 block">
          <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/Aa8c317d768c143bf98a8a63a6a5de8f34.png" alt="Lab Coats" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500 opacity-60" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-6">
            <h3 class="text-white font-black text-xl mb-1">Lab Coats</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">Professional physician coats</p>
            <span class="mt-2 text-secondary text-xs font-bold group-hover:underline">Browse →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-[3/4] bg-secondary block">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center">
            <span class="text-5xl mb-4">✨</span>
            <h3 class="text-white font-black text-xl mb-2">Custom OEM/ODM / Private Label</h3>
            <p class="text-emerald-100 text-sm mb-4">Build your own brand with Yilong manufacturing</p>
            <span class="bg-white text-secondary font-bold px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-sm">Start Your Project →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== MODULE 5: FAQ ==================== -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-4">Common Questions</div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-900">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="font-black text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-secondary font-black text-xs mt-1">Q:</span>
              I want to build my own brand, but MOQ is too high. What can I do?
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed pl-6 border-l-2 border-secondary/30">
              <strong class="text-slate-800">Answer:</strong> Our Color MOQ is 10 sets/color, and Logo customization starts from 20 sets/style — far below the industry norm of 50–200 sets/color. You can mix sizes freely within each color. For example, 10 sets of Navy can be: XS×2, S×3, M×3, L×2. We have a dedicated "small brand incubation program" — most of our US clients started exactly like this. Talk to us and we will find a way.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="font-black text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-secondary font-black text-xs mt-1">Q:</span>
              Can your quality match FIGs?
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed pl-6 border-l-2 border-secondary/30">
              <strong class="text-slate-800">Answer:</strong> Our 205 GSM Premium fabric is formulated to match the hand-feel of FIGs' signature fabric — soft, four-way stretch, and comfortable for long shifts. It passes OEKO-TEX® Standard 100 certification, color fastness Grade 4–5/5, and 40+ wash cycle durability tests (SGS tested). We currently do OEM for several US D2C scrub brands. Contact us to request sample pricing and lead time.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="font-black text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-secondary font-black text-xs mt-1">Q:</span>
              How long for samples? What's the minimum order quantity?
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed pl-6 border-l-2 border-secondary/30">
              <strong class="text-slate-800">Answer:</strong> Samples in 7 working days. Production in 15–30 working days depending on order volume. Color MOQ is 10 sets/color (sizes can be freely mixed). Logo customization starts from 20 sets/style. We support "sample first, then production order" — see the quality before committing.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="font-black text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-secondary font-black text-xs mt-1">Q:</span>
